18:
OF COURSE NOOOT!
But s-save your pity!
23:
Look, I think this is all just a big 
misunderstanding. We only 
just met Soushiro a minute 
ago.
24:
It's okay. Stella's not, uh... 
y'know?
I don't know how to say this 
with him standing right there...
29:
EEP?! Shhh!
I-I have n-NO idea what you 
m-mean! Ahaha...ha...
31:
Grrr, I have had enough! 
Enough!
35:
I shall spare you this time, but 
do not presume you have won! 
I WILL get Soushiro next—
39:
I-I mean, I will get YOU next 
time!
42:
You shall regret making an 
enemy of Inaho Tamamo! Bye!
48:
Wait! We were supposed to 
catch her!
...I completely forgot.
56:
She didn't seem like a bad 
person, did she?
62:
Not at all. She is a very sweet 
girl.
64:
Now, where have my manners 
gone? I have yet to introduce 
myself. My name is Soushiro 
Kengyu, a simple samurai.
66:
You have my gratitude for your 
aid. May I invite you inside for 
refreshments? It would be the 
least I can do to thank you.
70:
You travelled here from 
another world? That must 
have been quite the 
adventure.
73:
You believe us? ...That's a new 
feeling.
76:
The people of Yamato are no 
strangers to the idea of other 
worlds, what with the yokai's 
arrival from the West.
78:
What concerns me is that you 
were sent here by the Diviners' 
Commission.
80:
If you aim to capture Inaho, 
I am afraid I—
84: I don't want to capture her.
85:
I would like to try speaking 
with her again.
89:
Yeah, I think we're all with 
Stella here.
Forget the diviners.
92:
That is very reassuring to hear, 
my feline yokai friend.
100:
My apologies. Either way, if you 
wish to speak with Inaho, you 
may find her at the shrine just 
west of here. Simply follow the 
stairs.
102:
There was a petal caught in 
her hair—and the shrine is the 
only place I know where cherry 
blossoms bloom year-round.
107:
That sounds like a promising 
lead. Thank you, Soushiro.
110:
Yeah! And thank you for 
having us over for tea. It was 
really good!
116:
It was a pleasure to have you. 
Take care, and feel free to stop 
by any time.
120:
Oh. Just now, was that—
Hmm...
